{"tid":2174864,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"17 歲男生藏摺刀及鎚子 遭控嚴重罪名 開審前撤控改守行為","createTime":"2020-08-26T07:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T07:32:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a8394574f93aaaefb0dcdb9ac8870dbdff82b3a","tid":2174864,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:13:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/UYIX7TC4CREBDMMSW332NF6VUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FUYIX7TC4CREBDMMSW332NF6VUY%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=082fd3ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FUYIX7TC4CREBDMMSW332NF6VUY%2F&h=1a856502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/UYIX7TC4CREBDMMSW332NF6VUY/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年聖誕節期間，網民發起於多個商場「和你shop」，及後旺角朗豪坊發生警民衝突。17 歲男生當日被警方截查，搜出摺刀及鎚子，原被控在《公安條例》下的在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，及後改控刑責更重的管有任何物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產罪。案件原定今早於西九龍裁判法院開審，惟控方終同意撤控，准被告在同意案情下，以1,500元自簽保守行為12個月。"},{"pid":"1c4feefeb97a51068c7126deac65da00a14e08b9","tid":2174864,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7e20af43b7ff3465751c5e298cc0fe70ff77f9","tid":2174864,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57974b36968e6ab97a949432849688a6e674624","tid":2174864,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:21:58.000Z","msg":"點解有咁大分別？<br />\n有啲手足釘到死<br />\n有啲手足最後無事<br />\n會唔會落口供情況導致？<br />\n睇案情好多蘇狗呢啲無乜特別都重判，又作故仔又盛都要砌到佢坐<br />\n即係案情影響不大？"},{"pid":"b584693c05e30a7d70848fa92879edcc057c2c4